    dc:description "FIGURES 40–44. Teleiopsis sharporum sp. nov. 40, 41. Adult. 40. Holotype. 41. Paratype, female (gen. slide 149/19, O. Bidzilya). 42. Male genitalia, paratype (gen. slide 22/19, O. Bidzilya). 43. Male abdominal segment VIII (gen. slide 22/19, O. Bidzilya). 44. Female abdominal segment VII: tergum (left), sternum (right) (gen. slide 183/20, O. Bidzilya)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4690595/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690599>
